      • createInstance

        public static <K,V> KeyedObjectFactory<K,V> createInstance(KeyedObjectFactory<K,V> factory,
                                           RetainPolicy policy)
        Creates new pool of object instances. Instances are created on demand. Created instances are stored in the pool and reused. Hard retain policy guarantees that the same instance is always return for the same key. Soft and weak policies can return different instances for the same key. With soft and weak policies only one instance for given key can be referenced at any point of time.
